{"tid":2329371,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朴軫永＋Rain的夢幻組合「換成我」：復古New Jazz Swing風潮再現","createTime":"2020-12-17T07:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T11:44:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e74046f3a164cbe6ac09225951f96740042fe724","tid":2329371,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_0b6b85658faf9eb6611b2caf3e8a38c5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-17/132400-889373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_0b6b85658faf9eb6611b2caf3e8a38c5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-17%2F132400-889373.jpg&h=1fd003a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手朴軫永與Rain共同登上時尚雜誌2021年的新年1月號封面人物。兩人超級不設限的動作姿勢以及超時尚表情，令人想起80、90年代的巴比布朗、Baby Face等歌手，更宣布兩人共組團體「換成我」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0b7d8bf00f1f70cc765e3355067d12d3/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-17/132400-889369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0b7d8bf00f1f70cc765e3355067d12d3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-17%2F132400-889369.jpg&h=15916529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為新歌填詞譜曲的朴軫永說：「去年智薰告訴我「在我年紀變得更大之前，想要好好地與哥一起站上舞台。」所以有了這次機會，雖然私下我們很熟，但正式的邀歌這還是第一次。」說明了兩人共組團體的來龍去脈。「想要表現與時下愛豆不同的概念，想展現80、90年代曾流行過的帥氣男性雙人組合。」朴軫永補充了造型上的概念。最近除了成功推出日本女偶像團體NiziU出道，朴軫永還在日本被選為2020年度人物，成為七人組男子樂團「Psypher」的製作人，再度展現幕後實力的Rain說：「Rap、唱功、舞蹈、詞曲創作等所有能力兼備的團隊，讓人期待感大增。而團隊名字是想與舞台下的對粉絲們更接近，並與舞台上展現具有暗號的強烈表現，具有很深遠的意義。」<br />\n<br />\n朴軫永與Rain對於所有的照片被後製成為二次梗圖或動圖這件事，他們覺得只希望自己多多增加親和力，希望能成為人們的安慰，這樣才是真正的藝人。兩人也在拍攝現場隨著新曲跳舞，完美又天衣無縫的搭配簡直是夢幻組合。請粉絲們繼續期待朴軫永跟Rain的新作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4e30af06264c44f1bc57346dd7532403/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-17/132400-889372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4e30af06264c44f1bc57346dd7532403%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-17%2F132400-889372.jpg&h=77e06c57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e18f87b2e54974606a01660305380467d9801035","tid":2329371,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"很有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0942e0f3325852c9c1cab120f4485660afd53de9","tid":2329371,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"2條過氣油炸鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ac40cc574f9f25fdf21526d62983d881344243","tid":2329371,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0942e0f3325852c9c1cab120f4485660afd53de9","tid":2329371,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"2條過氣油炸鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:02:27.000Z","msg":"Shut the hell up<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef46449d76f6d89ee5242a5c5abd1b9805c1818","tid":2329371,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e18f87b2e54974606a01660305380467d9801035","tid":2329371,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"很有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:02:42.000Z","msg":"Daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dan